ActPublic Service Employment Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Federal Economic Development Agency for Northern Ontario as a Department and the President as Deputy Head of that Agency for the Purposes of that Act
PrecisOrder (1) designating the Federal Economic Development Agency for Northern Ontario as a department for the purposes of the Public Service Employment Act; and (2) designating its President as the deputy head of that Agency for the purposes of the Act.
